NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|What you might, at trick 5, do is put up the @D10 when you lead a diamond. That works when I have the @DJ. It is unlikely I have the @DAK, as I would play one of them when you lead a low diamond off dummy. So the @DQ is very unlikely to do any good.|
