NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Also, you got expert defense on this hand. Most declarers would make because my hand would lead a diamond rather than a spade. And you would either get a diamond ruff, or score your @DQ. You were unlucky to be playing against Sandy and me :).|
